description.en:
Eren Yeager Inu is an anime based token, based on Eren Yeager, the main protagonist in Attack on Titan. 
Since anime tokens are trending, we decided to envolved the well-known Attack on Titan, a Japanese manga serie. One of our goals is to bring the Eren Yeager fans to create a great community around that.
Our utility involves a play-to-earn game, which will be launched on our website, with wallet integration included.
